description._content: Gottlieb, William P., 1917-, photographer. [Portrait of Dardanelle, Joe Sinacore, and Bert Nazer, Sheraton Hotel, Satire Room(?), New York, N.Y., ca. June 1946] 1 negative : b&w ; 3 1/4 x 4 1/4 in. Gottlieb Forms part of: William P. Gottlieb Collection (Library of Congress). In: "Dardanelle is versatile," Down Beat, v. 13, no. 13 (June 17, 1946), p. 13. Subjects: Dardanelle Sinacore, Joe Nazer, Bert Jazz musicians--1940-1950. Women jazz musicians--1940-1950. Pianists--1940-1950. Double bassists--1940-1950. Guitarists--1940-1950.
